这个 Lua 程序运行在 OpenResty 中，用于向 FastDFS 上传图片。

Requirements
============

* fastdfs [ https://github.com/happyfish100/fastdfs ]
* lua 5.1
* OpenResty [ https://openresty.org/ ]
* lua-resty-fastdfs [ https://github.com/azurewang/lua-resty-fastdfs ]
* ImageMagick [ https://github.com/leafo/magick ] required by thumb


  Here's how to install magick on Fedora Linux:

  $ sudo dnf install ImageMagick-devel
  $ wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leafo/magick/master/magick/init.lua -O framework/magick.lua

How to run this app
===================

$ mkdir logs
$ sudo /usr/local/openresty/nginx/sbin/nginx -p `pwd` -c nginx.conf


To upload, visit this page

  http://localhost:8080/

or use curl:

  $ curl -v -0 -F "file=@123.txt" localhost:8080/upload


Appending is supported:

  $ curl -v -0 -F "file=@456.txt" localhost:8080/upload/group1/M00/00/02/wKgBtFY8BW2ETBr0AAAAAFqCAvc159.txt

  or

  $ curl -v -0 -F "append=group1/M00/00/02/wKgBtFY8BW2ETBr0AAAAAFqCAvc159.txt" -F "file=@456.txt" localhost:8080/upload

